description: Look at the cables for any sign of damage, outcome="NOMINAL\n\nFeedback: All inspected cables show no observable signs of internal fault or external damage. All visible cable ports are securely connected, and no ruptures or physical anomalies have been reported in any cable segment assessed. Portions of the cables routed inside the Control Cube and Load Cube remain uninspected, so faults in those concealed areas cannot be ruled out with this visual check alone. However, based on all available observations, there are no signs of 'CablesRuptured' at this stage.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.", precise_action_cost=80.0, cost_breakdown=[('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0)], simplified_outcome=None), DiagnosticActionResult(action=
